{"tid":2191222,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：在現代商場唱港獨歌，或做抗爭運動，會被觀察及拍攝記錄。偽港獨派笑我教席保不住，有其他學者出聲提醒你嗎？","createTime":"2020-09-06T10:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T05:32:25.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75a12c44031b2f74bd06ca0885b3797b6b161f05","tid":2191222,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/建築的實用與美學-被監視的囚徒大合唱/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%A6%E7%94%A8%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%B8-%E8%A2%AB%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9A%E5%BE%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%90%88%E5%94%B1%2F&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4luXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=142cec4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%A6%E7%94%A8%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%B8-%E8%A2%AB%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9A%E5%BE%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%90%88%E5%94%B1%2F&h=9ba51eec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/建築的實用與美學-被監視的囚徒大合唱/</a><br />\n...<br />\n陳雲：在現代商場，由於訪客是走動的，故此訪客也同時可以觀察其他人及瀏覽對面的商店，但如果你站定不動而唱港獨歌，或者試圖在裡面做抗爭運動，你的一舉一動都會被觀察及拍攝記錄。<br />\n這也是大台的建立地方。只要有人站在商場的透視中心點，用擴音器法號司令，就得到各方矚目，建立了大台。你除了呼應說好high之外，無法發言的。<br />\n（後記：你在商場唱港獨歌的時候，香港有社會學家或其他學者出聲提醒你嗎？除了陳雲，無囉。所以我被大學解僱囉。偽港獨派好多笑我連教席都保不住，怎樣保住香港的啊。）<br />\n..."},{"pid":"e7e63f9ba0babd57727cda3567f4d0671e0ae207","tid":2191222,"uid":300165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75a12c44031b2f74bd06ca0885b3797b6b161f05","tid":2191222,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/建築的實用與美學-被監視的囚徒大合唱/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%A6%E7%94%A8%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%B8-%E8%A2%AB%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9A%E5%BE%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%90